*Pola* sata sam provela u trčanju (I spent half an hour running).
*Pola* sam sata čekala da se dogovorimo (I waited half an hour to settle).
*Pola* godine sam se bavio tim poslom (I was dealing with that job for half a year).
*Pola* svog života sam provela u Beogradu (I spent half of my life in Belgrade).
*Pola* sata sam proveo učeći (I spent half an hour studying).